conduct more aggressively than previous administrations.

Perhaps counterintuitively, given his concern over legal cases being influe=
nced by outside media attention, Hochman told me he=E2=80=99s in favor of r=
eintroducing cameras into L.A. courtrooms, a practice that=E2=80=99s dwindl=
ed since the eight-month-long O.J. trial enraptured international audiences=
=2E =E2=80=9CBeing able to hear and see wh=
at goes on in a courtroom, I think,=
