s</i>, which explores the severe abuse they allegedly suffered at the hands=
 of their father, <b>Jos=C3=A9</b>, a former RCA Records executive. Indeed,=
 the question on everyone=E2=80=99s mind=E2=80=94from folks at CAA to Uber =
